6c37a5469bc982f6247183","tid":1580303,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnLxWAc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnLxWAc.jpg&h=5ea06781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2Leqwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2Leqwm.jpg&h=6f74c0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期： 9月21日 時間：2:00集合，3點起步<br />\n路線：新和里  -&gt; 屯門政府合署<br />\n<br />\n屯門公園<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">(一)禁打賞</span><br />\n 要求修改《遊樂場地規例》，禁止一切在公園範圍內涉及任何形式金錢之打賞，行乞，捐贈行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">(二)投訴權</span><br />\n 呼籲立法會民政事務委員會各委員正視民意，盡快修訂《遊樂場地規》使附近街坊同樣擁有投訴權利<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(三)加強執法</span><br />\n 要求康文署增加合資格執法人員及簡化檢控程序，加強執法及檢控違法行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(四)正視設施不足</span><br />\n 要求康文署及屯門區議會，正視區內老人文娛設施不足問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">(五)檢討管理</span><br />\n 要求康文署檢討屯門公園及割下公共空間的管理，有效分配公園及其他公共空間的使用權<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\n巴士： <br />\n58M / 58X / 63X / 260X / 960 - 紅橋站落車<br />\n黨鐵：<br />\n1. 西鐵兆康站落車<br />\n2. 轉乘輕鐵 751 (往友愛）或610 （往屯門碼頭）"},{"pid":"464faee155334cccc8a1f3590a36e31f3c00e9a3","tid":1580303,"uid":185045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"到時一定會係socalled公開但門口周圍一堆防暴唔俾示威者抗議表達訴求"},{"pid":"9c49acb45c660f0f646fb758402eea1e3e100535","tid":1580303,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"咪撚去啦屌<br />\n冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初比哂機會都唔對話<br />\n依家仲比機會佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"